---
title: Central American Style Spiced BBQ Beef Chilli with Rice and Cheese
description: On the table in less than 25 minutes, this Central American Style Spiced BBQ Beef Chilli is quick but still full of flavour. Central American style spice mix drives the flavour here for a simple dinner that suits everyone's tastes.
